How to run the server:
    php -S localhost:80 server.php

Notes:
    - All countries follow ISO-3166-alpha-2 format guidelines

GET /search?q={string}
    - Search NPOs that match {string}
    - {string} must be at least 3 chars in length
    - {string} must be url encoded

GET /{npo_slug}
GET /portugal/abraco
GET /portugal/abraco/volunteering-opportunities
GET /portugal/abraco/volunteering-opportunities/1
GET /portugal/abraco/volunteering-opportunities/1/volunteers
GET /portugal/abraco/donations
POST /portugal/abraco/donate

GET /causes
GET /causes/{id}
GET /causes/1/npos
GET /causes/1/volunteering-opportunities

GET /volunteering-opportunities

GET /me
GET /me/badges
GET /me/donations
GET /me/volunteering-opportunities

GET /badges

POST /register
POST /login
